label: Caution
text: USE PROTECTIVE GLOVES WHEN HANDLING CHEMICALS. CONTACT WITH SKIN CAN CAUSE IRRITATION OR BURNS.

label: Warning
text: DO NOT OPERATE MACHINERY WITHOUT PROPER TRAINING. IMPROPER USE CAN RESULT IN SERIOUS INJURY OR DEATH.

label: Caution
text: WEAR SAFETY GLASSES TO PROTECT YOUR EYES FROM FLYING DEBRIS. FAILURE TO DO SO CAN RESULT IN EYE INJURY.

label: Warning
text: KEEP FLAMMABLE MATERIALS AWAY FROM OPEN FLAMES. IGNITION CAN CAUSE FIRE OR EXPLOSION.

label: Caution
text: ENSURE PROPER VENTILATION WHEN USING SOLVENTS. INHALATION CAN CAUSE RESPIRATORY ISSUES.

label: Warning
text: DO NOT REMOVE SAFETY GUARDS FROM EQUIPMENT. REMOVAL CAN RESULT IN SERIOUS INJURY.

label: Caution
text: USE EAR PROTECTION IN HIGH NOISE AREAS. EXPOSURE TO LOUD NOISE CAN CAUSE HEARING LOSS.

label: Warning
text: DO NOT TOUCH LIVE ELECTRICAL WIRES. CONTACT CAN RESULT IN ELECTROCUTION.

label: Caution
text: STORE HEAVY OBJECTS ON LOWER SHELVES TO PREVENT FALLING. FALLING OBJECTS CAN CAUSE INJURY.

label: Warning
text: BEFORE YOU START WORK, YOU MUST PUT ON A SAFETY HARNESS AND ATTACH IT TO THE ACCESS PLATFORM. WITHOUT A SAFETY HARNESS, YOU CAN FALL. THIS CAN KILL YOU OR CAUSE YOU INJURY.
